{"tid":1599460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍屍今朝手持五星旗去金紫荊廣場影合照","createTime":"2019-09-28T03:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T04:02:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e9b177c8310b4c1d8e1307a4a5472cd460cbf3","tid":1599460,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/epnaQd8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FepnaQd8.png&h=cbe1a2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQ5f1kU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQ5f1kU.png&h=1f9b69ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民今早發起「我和國旗合個影」，在金紫荊廣場外與國旗拍照留影，現場有數十名市民手持小幅五星旗揮舞，並與一面大國旗合照，期間有一隊軍裝警員巡邏行經。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，為慶祝中共建政70周年，內地共青團日前發布「我和國旗合個影」主題活動，呼籲人民愛國不要猶豫，踴躍在網路社群平台上傳與五星旗合影的照片、影片，發出愛國強音。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2262534/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2262534%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=f3d8456d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2262534/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d92cb80cbda70f56e481f0d74a65b76adc89cb","tid":1599460,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"關我撚事？佢哋根本叫唔醒"},{"pid":"605362a0132b269e6f0af7a655b3ab7213f6d4b5","tid":1599460,"uid":148332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"目測300萬人"},{"pid":"dd2fa59f271af05cafe27288a5b966908593c35e","tid":1599460,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"散播愛支病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed0c82a98a8f2a9c86f62b839a7bf05659850fe","tid":1599460,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT